-- Pound Declines Versus Dollar, Dropping 0.2 Percent to $1.5210
-- B y   D a v i d   G o o d m a n
-- 2013-04-05T07:10:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-05/pound-declines-versus-dollar-dropping-0-2-percent-to-1-5210.html
The pound declined against the
dollar for the first time in three days, dropping 0.2 percent to
$1.5210 as of 8:09 a.m. London time.  It was little changed at 84.85 pence per euro.  To contact the reporter on this story:
